<h2 id="翻译" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#翻译" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 翻译</h2>
<h4 id="i-wasn-t-born-in-this-country-i-didn-t-grow-up-in-any-one-particular-religion-i-have-a-mixed-race-background-and-i-m-gay" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#i-wasn-t-born-in-this-country-i-didn-t-grow-up-in-any-one-particular-religion-i-have-a-mixed-race-background-and-i-m-gay" aria-hidden="true">#</a> I wasn't born in this country. I didn't grow up in any one particular religion. I have a mixed race background, and I'm gay.</h4>
